<paragraph id="IFRS15_123" base="F31716676"><paranum>123</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 15"/><data name="paranum" value="123"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS15_P0477">An entity shall disclose the judgements, and changes in the judgements, made in applying this Standard that significantly affect the determination of the amount and timing of <xref base="F31716759" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_P0508">revenue<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0341"/></ph></xref> from <xref base="SL31717224" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_P0498">contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0049"/></ph></xref> with <xref base="F31716740" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_P0502">customers<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_customer"/></ph></xref>. In particular, an entity shall explain the judgements, and changes in the judgements, used in determining both of the following:</p><ol id="IFRS15_L0051" base="F31716678" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p id="IFRS15_P0478" base="F31716679">the timing of satisfaction of <xref base="F31716748" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_P0504">performance obligations<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0288"/></ph></xref> (see <xref id="IFRS15_X0551" base="F33213366" href="IFRS15_124.dita#IFRS15_124">paragraphs 124&#x2013;125</xref>); and</p>       </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p id="IFRS15_P0479" base="F31716681">the <xref base="F31716779" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_P0510">transaction price<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0370"/></ph></xref> and the amounts allocated to performance obligations (see <xref id="IFRS15_X0552" base="F33213367" href="IFRS15_126.dita#IFRS15_126">paragraph 126</xref>).</p>       </li></ol></body></paragraph>